The '''sparrows''' are a religious movement that arose within the ranks of the [[Faith of the Seven]]. It is composed of the lowest and humblest of the Holy Faith, and was formed in response to the suffering inflicted on the [[smallfolk]] of Westeros during the [[War of the Five Kings]].

They are led by the so-called High Sparrow, a travelling [[Septon]].
